## üî≠ Projects I'm Working On

### [RZ1 Portfolio Website](https://github.com/THE-RZ1-x/portfolio_rz1)
A modern, interactive personal portfolio website built with React and Vite, featuring terminal-style animations and professional CV presentation.

![Portfolio Screenshot](https://github.com/THE-RZ1-x/portfolio_rz1/raw/main/path/to/screenshot.png)

**Features**:
- Terminal-style typing animation
- Interactive CV page with progress bars
- Professional two-column layout
- Responsive design for all devices
- Neon theme with modern aesthetics
- Framer Motion animations
- Dynamic routing
- Social media integration

**Tech Stack**:
- React 18+
- Vite
- Styled Components
- Framer Motion
- React Router DOM
- React Icons

**Live Site**: [RZ1 Portfolio](https://the-rz1-x.github.io/portfolio_rz1/)

